<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Bienvenue sur Trackr</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8f8f8; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f8f8f8;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 48px 24px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="520" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="max-width: 520px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 32px 40px 24px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td valign="middle" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                    <img src="https://cdn.trackrr.app/images/branding/trackr-logo.png" alt="Trackr" width="28" height="32" style="display: block;" />
                  </td>
                  <td valign="middle">
                    <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #955ae9; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Trackr</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
                Bienvenue sur Trackr
              </h1>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.6;">
                Salut {{ displayName }}, merci d'avoir rejoint Trackr. Tu es prêt à suivre tes lectures.
              </p>

              <div style="margin: 32px 0; padding: 24px; background-color: #fafafa; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a;">
                  Pour commencer
                </p>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="36" valign="top">
                      <img src="https://cdn.trackrr.app/images/branding/icon-book.png" alt="" width="24" height="24" style="display: block;" />
                    </td>
                    <td valign="top">
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.5;">
                        <strong>Ajoute des livres</strong> à ta bibliothèque et organise ta collection
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="36" valign="top">
                      <img src="https://cdn.trackrr.app/images/branding/icon-chart.png" alt="" width="24" height="24" style="display: block;" />
                    </td>
                    <td valign="top">
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.5;">
                        <strong>Suis ta progression</strong> et consulte tes statistiques de lecture
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="36" valign="top">
                      <img src="https://cdn.trackrr.app/images/branding/icon-users.png" alt="" width="24" height="24" style="display: block;" />
                    </td>
                    <td valign="top">
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.5;">
                        <strong>Connecte-toi avec des lecteurs</strong> et partage tes avis
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>

              <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
                <a href="https://trackrr.app" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #955ae9; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">
                  Ouvrir Trackr
                </a>
              </div>

              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #888888; line-height: 1.6;">
                Si tu as des questions, réponds simplement à cet email. On est là pour t'aider.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px 32px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #888888; line-height: 1.5;">
                Cet email a été envoyé par Trackr. Pour toute question, contacte-nous à <a href="mailto:support@trackrr.app" style="color: #955ae9; text-decoration: none;">support@trackrr.app</a>
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa;">
                © 2026 Trackr · <a href="https://trackrr.app/privacy" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">Confidentialité</a> · <a href="https://trackrr.app/terms" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">Conditions</a>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
